Talent Description:
---
When hit with an element, take reduced damage from said element, but take more damage from any other element.
What It Does In-Game:
---
When hit by an element, you get +20% **damage reduction** towards that element for every new hit, you lose the dmg reduction once hit by other elements. The *first hit by new elements* deals 25% extra dmg to you, but the next hits by that same element gain +20% **damage reduction**. Dodging and parrying any elements is treated the same as being hit by them.

Talent Category:
---
Caster
Talent Description:
---
When hit with an element, take reduced damage from said element, but take more damage from any other element.
What It Does In-Game:
---
When hit by an element, you get +20% **damage reduction** towards that element for every new hit, you lose the dmg reduction once hit by other elements. The *first hit by new elements* deals 25% dmg to you, but the next hits by that same element gain +20% **damage reduction**. Dodging and parrying any elements is treated the same as being hit by them.
Requirements (if known):
---
15 Intelligence
Locks Out: Return to the Dark Ages
Talent Stats:
---
+7 Carry Load, +2 Elemental Intensity
Talent Image:
---
![Everchanging Aegis](https://i.gyazo.com/d3a9c710579151799dbd701c08f232a9.png)
